		Contains all 'Arabic Roots' for the 'Arabic Letter'.
		Contains all 'Entries' for each 'Arabic Root', or references to other 'Roots'.
		Contains the content of the Lexicion in form of 'Senses', which might be grouped in 'Homographs' (called 'Dissiciations' by EWL).
		Contains all 'Senses', which belong to the same 'Homograph' (optional).
		Contains the textual content of the Lexicion.
