Hence, [it is said to be] applied to water, as meaning Cool, or cold: (TA:) or, so applied, sweet: (Ṣ:) or sweet, clear, or limpid, pure, easy in its descent, that slips into the throat; 
as also zulaAzilN↓: (TA:) or quick in its descent and passage in the throat, (Ḳ,* TA,) cool, or cold, sweet, clear, or limpid, easy in its descent; 
